Commander, 

The end of Balthazar was the beginning of a new threat to our region. Please find enclosed a classified report prepared for your eyes only, using intelligence gained from confidential maginamic experts.

—Kito

I'm sure you're aware of the recent Awakened attacks near large cities in Tyria. I have a plan to track their portal aperture positions to allow Peacemakers to intercept them more easily, but I need assistance. Please meet me at your home at your earliest convenience.

—Ninn

—Mission: protect gift dolyaks from malfunctioning toys.

—Survive all ten rounds to win.

—Destroy trees and buildings to get bundles that can be used to build defenses.

—Scrap and snow bundles allow you to place and upgrade turrets and barriers.

—You can only heal by standing in the center of the map.

—Hay appears every two waves and can be used to heal gift dolyaks.

This adds a garden to your home instance, which can be planted to grow four harvesting resource nodes from a wide variety of available options. Additional planting options can be collected by gathering seeds from harvesting nodes in the open world. Rare nodes from the Black Lion Chest and underwater plants are not included.
